      "title": "Upscaler Filename - Image + Video example",
      "properties": {
        "widget_ue_connectable": {}
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "## Upscaler Filename example\n\nThis workflow shows two ready-to-use branches:\n\n### VIDEO BRANCH\n`VHS_LoadVideo → Upscale Model Loader with Filename → ImageUpscaleWithModel → ImageScale → Video Combine`\n\n### IMAGE BRANCH\n`Load Image → Upscale Model Loader with Filename → ImageUpscaleWithModel → ImageScale → Save Image`\n\nHow to use:\n- Select an upscaler in **Upscale Model Loader with Filename**.\n- The image/video filename prefixes update automatically from the selected model name.\n- For video, keep `Video Combine` enabled and mute/bypass `Save Image`.\n- For image, keep `Save Image` enabled and mute/bypass `Video Combine`.\n\nNote: `filename_prefix` widgets on the final save nodes are converted to inputs so they can receive the generated strings."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
